<p>I'm using NHibernate as Orm Mapper. I have 2 Classes, ClassA and ClassB. ClassA has a Property of Type ClassB and ClassB has a Property of Type ClassA! These should be backed by only one Database Column! And If I fill Property on one of the Classes, the other should also be filled! Is this possible with NHibernate?</p>  <p>Mapping of ClassA</p>  <pre><code>References(x =&gt; x.ClassB, "ClassBId").Cascade.SaveUpdate().Unique();       </code></pre>  <p>Mapping of ClassB</p>  <pre><code>HasOne(x =&gt; x.ClassA).PropertyRef(x =&gt; x.ClassB).Cascade.SaveUpdate(); </code></pre>  <p>What I want is, that the Classes are Synchronized, without reloading!</p>